dRAC portable bundle

Commit: @DRACTWEAK_GIT_SHA@
Platform: Windows x64

Contents:
- dractest.exe
- Runtime DLLs required to launch the executable on a typical Windows machine

Usage:
1. Extract this zip to a writable directory.
2. Run dractest.exe.
3. Use Ethernet on Windows. FireWire is not part of the Windows release flow.

Build notes:
- This bundle was produced from the dractweak repository using the dractest_package target.
- The application is built with the Windows MSVC preset and the Ethernet-only Amp1394 configuration.
